graph TD
    A[User Input & Conversation History] --> B[Middleware: Message Trimmer]
    
    subgraph Execution Context
    B -->|Keeps System Prompt & Last N Messages| C[Core LLM Node]
    
    C -->|Invokes Tool with args| D[Tool Node]
    
    E[Graph Config / State] -.->|Injects Runtime Variables implicitly| D
    end
    
    D -->|Returns Result| C
    C --> F[Final State Update]
    
    subgraph The Problem Solved
    G[Long History = Token Limits & Hallucinations]
    H[LLM Guessing Variables = Security Risk]
    end
    
    B -.->|Solves| G
    E -.->|Solves| H
